V0602_01_00_00_0.text:
The name is Soulburner.
The one sending you home in ashes!

V0602_01_00_01_0.text:
Sounds fun.
I'm ready to Duel!

V0602_01_00_02_0.text:
I don't have time for this!
I'll burn you quick!

V0602_01_00_03_0.text: As long as I stick to my strategies, I know I'll win!

V0602_01_00_04_0.text: The pain of my past won't hold me back!

V0602_01_00_05_0.text: Just like Playmaker, Dueling's my life.

V0602_01_00_05_1.text: So I may be a tiiiiiny bit stronger than you think.

V0602_01_00_06_0.text: Let's set this Duel on fire, Playmaker!

V0602_01_00_07_0.text:
I can't believe I get to Duel my hero!
Let's go, Gore!

V0602_01_00_08_0.text:
Wow!
I'm gonna Duel the megastar who saved LINK VRAINS!

V0602_01_00_09_0.text: Don't even think about letting me win, Varis!

V0602_01_00_10_0.text: Human or AI - this battle is between me and you!

V0602_03_00_00_0.text: Time to set this Duel aflame!

V0602_03_00_05_0.text:
I survived to this moment...
The moment I win!

V0602_05_00_00_0.text:
I can't lose!
I have too much to fight for!

V0602_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0602_07_09_01_0.text: This is the card I Set!

V0602_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon my monster in Defense Position!

V0602_11_10_01_0.text: I blaze the circuit that scorches the path to the future!

V0602_11_10_02_0.text: I blaze the circuit that scorches the path to the future!

V0602_11_10_02_1.text:
I set my monsters in the Link Arrows!
Link the circuit!

V0602_21_00_01_0.text: Aww, I thought I'd win this Duel by now...

V0602_21_00_03_0.text: Let's see what you can do.

V0602_21_00_04_0.text: If I don't give up, I still have a chance!

V0602_21_00_05_0.text:
It's not looking good for me...
But it could be worse!

V0602_28_00_01_0.text:
I'm glad you didn't hold back.
It made the Duel great!

V0602_28_00_02_0.text: I know you don't want to lose, but I can't afford to either.

V0602_28_00_03_0.text: Flame is the greatest friend anyone can ever have.

V0602_28_00_03_1.text: He and Playmaker are why I'm standing here today!

V0602_28_00_04_0.text:
I did it...
I actually did it...
I defeated Playmaker!

V0602_28_00_05_0.text:
You're my hero, Gore.
But I couldn't let you stop me!

V0602_28_00_06_0.text:
Did you change your avatar?
This one's awesome!

V0602_28_00_06_1.text: Maybe I should change my avatar too.

V0602_28_00_07_0.text: You created this mess, so make sure it never happens again.

V0602_28_00_07_1.text: I order you to stop anyone who stirs up trouble.

V0602_28_00_08_0.text:
You’re not a better Duelist than Flame.
Or a better friend!

V0602_28_00_08_1.text: Our two minds are a billion times greater than yours!

V0602_29_00_00_0.text: You knew every move I was gonna make...

V0602_29_00_03_0.text: That's why you're the best, Playmaker!

V0602_29_00_04_0.text: I may've lost, but it was amazing that I got to Duel you!

V0602_29_00_05_0.text: I see why you're the most popular celebrity in LINK VRAINS!

V0602_29_00_06_0.text: You're not a great person, but you are a great Duelist.

V0602_29_00_07_0.text:
Sorry, Flame...
I let you down...

V0602_33_00_01_0.text: If you're gonna stand in my way, you're gonna get burnt!

V0602_33_00_02_0.text: Flame and I are bringin' the heat!

V0602_33_00_03_1.text:
I'll set the world aflame!
Burning Draw!

V0602_33_00_04_1.text:
Ready to witness a miracle?
Burning Draw!

V0602_30_00_02_0.text: Oh. That's nothing to worry about.

V0602_34_00_00_0.text: Are you making fun of me?

V0602_34_00_02_0.text: I never thought you'd resort to dirty tricks.

V0602_34_00_03_0.text:
Ahh... Ahhhhh!
Stop it!
I can't take it anymore!

V0602_34_00_05_0.text: My heart's on fire! Burning Draw!

V0602_34_00_06_0.text: This isn't a cool way to win!

V0602_34_00_07_0.text: What am I supposed to say to everyone who got me this far?

V0602_34_00_08_0.text:
I can't give up...
What would Flame think of me if I do?

V0602_34_00_09_0.text: This is between me and you!

V0602_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links!
It's time to link into the VRAINS!

V0602_35_00_00_0.text:
The name's Soulburner.
I'll torch anyone who gets in my way!

V0602_35_00_01_0.text:
My deck's ready!
It's time to link into the VRAINS!

V0602_36_00_02_0.text: Sorry... I know you can turn this around!

V0602_36_00_05_0.text: Maybe you have an answer, Playmaker!

Be reborn!
Link 2 Salamangreat Sunlight Wolf!

Let the flames engulf your body!
From its ashes, be reborn!

V0602_46_00_03_0.text: I blaze the circuit that scorches the path to the future!

V0602_46_00_04_0.text: I blaze the circuit that scorches the path to the future!

V0602_47_00_04_0.text:
You're your whole new self!
Link 1 Salamangreat Almiraj!

V0602_37_00_06_0.text: The scorching dragon that incinerates the sky!

V0602_47_00_06_0.text: Be reborn, Rank 4 Salamangreat Blaze Dragon!

V0602_37_00_07_0.text: This wild steed blazes the tundra to torch every illusion!

V0602_37_00_08_0.text: When the flames consume the old, a new creature emerges!

V0602_26_00_02_0.text: I'll get you back for that!
